"Per-core" = "コアごと";
"P = Performance cores (faster, higher power). E = Efficiency cores (slower, lower power). macOS assigns which core handles each workload automatically. On Intel Macs all cores are equivalent and show as Core N." = "P = Performanceコア（高速・高消費電力）。E = Efficiencyコア（低速・低消費電力）。どのコアが各処理を担当するかはmacOSが自動的に割り当てます。IntelのMacではすべてのコアが同等で、Core Nと表示されます。";
